B.NY={"i'm just browsing, thanks.":0,"i'm good for now, thanks.":1,"i'll let you know if i need anything.":2,"i'm just looking around, thanks.":3,"i'll ask if i need any help.":4,[u.f]:5,"i'll come back later, thanks.":6,"i'll think about it and come back.":7,"i'll take another look later.":8,"can i help you find anything?":9,[u.I]:10,"will do. thanks.":11,"sure, thank you.":12,"sounds good, thanks.":13,"hi, what can i get for you?":14,"could i get an iced latte, please?":15,"can i have an iced latte, please?":16,"i would like an iced latte, please.":17,"anything else?":18,"that's all, thank you.":19,"that will be all, thanks.":20,"i'm all set, thank you.":21,"are you ready to order?":22,"what do you recommend?":23,"what's popular here?":24,"what's your favorite dish?":25,"the grilled chicken is very popular.":26,"i'll have that, please.":27,"hi, how can i help you?":28,"i have a reservation under minji kim.":29,"i booked a room under minji kim.":30,"i'm checking in. the name is minji kim.":31,"i found it. may i see your passport?":32,"sure. here you go.":33,"hi, do you need some help?":34,"how do i get to the nearest subway station?":35,"is there a subway station nearby?":36,"could you point me to the nearest subway station?":37,"go straight and turn left at the corner.":38,"got it. thank you so much.":39,"where are you headed?":40,"could you take me to central station?":41,"central station, please.":42,"i'd like to go to central station.":43,"sure. it should take about twenty minutes.":44,"sounds good. thank you.":45,"hello, can i help you?":46,"could you tell me where gate twelve is?":47,"where can i find gate twelve?":48,"which way is gate twelve?":49,"it is down this hall on your right.":50,"is it far from here?":51,"hi, what can i help you with?":52,"do you have anything for a sore throat?":53,"i need something for a sore throat.":54,"could you recommend something for a sore throat?":55,"yes. do you have a fever?":56,"no, i don't have a fever.":57,"does the new process make sense?":58,"could you go over that one more time?":59,"could you explain that again?":60,"sorry, i missed that. could you repeat it?":61,"of course. i will show you step by step.":62,"that would be really helpful.":63,"hi, i do not think we have met.":64,"how do you know the host?":65,"so, how do you know everyone here?":66,"have you known the host for long?":67,"we used to work together. how about you?":68,"we met through a mutual friend.":69}
